1
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:28,180
♪Drifting aimlessly♪

2
00:00:29,180 --> 00:00:31,540
♪Not knowing where to go♪

3
00:00:31,780 --> 00:00:36,540
♪The moonlight tonight feels sorrowful♪

4
00:00:39,380 --> 00:00:42,260
♪I stand alone against it♪

5
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:44,620
♪But I don't want to♪

6
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:50,780
♪The longing catches me off guard♪

7
00:00:53,100 --> 00:00:58,380
♪To the silent night, I surrender myself♪

8
00:01:00,020 --> 00:01:01,500
♪Tossing and turning, lost in confusion♪

9
00:01:01,580 --> 00:01:10,620
♪In the darkness, I lose my way♪

10
00:01:28,180 --> 00:01:30,980
[Episode 1]

11
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:33,430
The world is full of danger,

12
00:01:34,160 --> 00:01:35,230
and the human mind is unpredictable.

13
00:01:36,080 --> 00:01:38,590
I just need

14
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,550
some precautions.

15
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:44,910
I'm a man.

16
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:47,390
Even if these photos leak,

17
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,630
[Fu Cheng]
it won't affect me at all.

18
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:52,950
Everyone has secrets that others don't know about.

19
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,350
And my secret is

20
00:01:56,680 --> 00:02:00,350
that I love watching virtuous ascetics lose control.

21
00:02:00,420 --> 00:02:02,620
[Jiang Yingxian, second daughter of Gangcheng's Jiang family]

22
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:03,830
Mr. Shen,

23
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:05,270
you can't go in.

24
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,790
The boss isn't available to meet other guests right now.

25
00:02:09,920 --> 00:02:11,950
Why, in such an embarrassing situation,

26
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,790
would you still...?

27
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,350
Stop talking.

28
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,710
Not available?

29
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,710
I didn't know she had guests today.

30
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,350
Mr. Shen.

31
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:28,590
What do you think of my lips?

32
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,190
Or do you

33
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,510
prefer my legs?

34
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,630
Why won't you let me in?

35
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:38,510
Is your boss doing something shady

36
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:40,550
in the room?

37
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:43,990
Mr. Shen.

38
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:49,990
Is that enough?

39
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,150
Pleasure working with you.

40
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,270
Mr. Shen.

41
00:02:56,620 --> 00:02:58,150
[Shen Dongyang, only son of Shen Ping, Nanli General Affairs Director,]

42
00:02:58,150 --> 00:02:59,100
[and Jiang Yingxian's fiancé]

43
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:03,940
[Bound by Sin]

44
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:07,900
[Haicheng Huanya Opera House]

45
00:03:08,340 --> 00:03:13,020
[Seven days ago]

46
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:14,190
Miss Jiang, look this way.

47
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:16,580
Miss Jiang, over here.

48
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,150
Mr. Shen is going too far,

49
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,270
giving your engagement necklace

50
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:24,150
to a random woman.

51
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:27,030
Is it really okay for me to wear your fiancée's

52
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:27,910
necklace?

53
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,230
Do whatever you want.

54
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:30,830
Mr. Shen is here.

55
00:03:31,300 --> 00:03:31,940
Mr. Shen has arrived.

56
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:32,500
Mr. Shen is here.

57
00:03:32,510 --> 00:03:33,460
- Mr. Shen. - Mr. Shen.

58
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:35,910
Mr. Shen, look this way.

59
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,790
Shen Dongyang and I are only engaged for business reasons.

60
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,300
We have no feelings for each other,

61
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,550
so I don't expect him to remain loyal to me.

62
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:45,310
But he's being so blatant about it.

63
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:48,430
What can I say? To gain more power, I need him around.

64
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,550
Are you sure Master Jiang

65
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,230
will let you be the head of the family

66
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:54,190
after you marry Mr. Shen?

67
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:58,550
Well, I have to take a leap of faith.

68
00:03:59,080 --> 00:03:59,630
By the way,

69
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:02,190
I left a document at the branch office.

70
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:03,350
Retrieve it for me.

71
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:05,670
Happy to help.

72
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,190
I've heard Miss Jiang really knows how to pull the strings,

73
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,510
and now half of the Jiang family's business

74
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:16,870
is under her control.

75
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:17,990
None of her brothers

76
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,070
can compare to her.

77
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,150
But I've also heard the Jiang family

78
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,830
is still looking for the illegitimate son they lost touch with.

79
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,510
So, who will eventually become head

80
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,990
of the Jiang family is still unclear.

81
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,790
Mr. Shen, Miss Jiang,

82
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:33,030
look this way.

83
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,870
Miss Jiang and Mr. Shen, you are such a perfect match.

84
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:35,790
Is your wedding

85
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,870
happening next year?

86
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,870
Yes, it seems so.

87
00:04:38,570 --> 00:04:39,370
A grand event is coming soon.

88
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,510
Covering the first floor.

89
00:04:46,020 --> 00:04:46,740
[Xu Yawei, daughter of Gangcheng's Xu family]
Covering the second floor.

90
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:47,820
Covering the third floor.

91
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:48,750
Alright,

92
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:49,430
return to your positions.

93
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:50,110
Yes, sir.

94
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,350
Ugh, she's so full of herself.

95
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,390
So she's got a fiancé. Big deal.

96
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,430
Without Shen Dongyang,

97
00:05:01,980 --> 00:05:02,890
she'd just be

98
00:05:03,060 --> 00:05:05,130
a useless rich girl who goes to the Orchid Club every night,

99
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:07,650
looking for random men to have fun with!

100
00:05:15,540 --> 00:05:16,170
Miss Xu,

101
00:05:16,860 --> 00:05:17,810
please watch your words.

102
00:05:28,740 --> 00:05:31,050
Since when is it your place

103
00:05:31,060 --> 00:05:32,090
to tell me what to do?

104
00:05:36,420 --> 00:05:37,490
Let me guess.

105
00:05:37,780 --> 00:05:41,530
You want to go please Jiang Yingxian too, don't you?

106
00:05:50,380 --> 00:05:51,050
Get out of the way.

107
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:53,130
Miss Xu.

108
00:05:53,780 --> 00:05:54,650
Stop following me.

109
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:57,210
Miss Xu.

110
00:05:57,380 --> 00:05:58,050
Stop following me!

111
00:05:58,580 --> 00:06:00,130
Miss Xu, don't go smoking opium again.

112
00:06:00,940 --> 00:06:01,770
Are you a dog?

113
00:06:04,060 --> 00:06:05,530
You follow me wherever I go.

114
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:09,690
I need to pee now. Are you going to follow me too?

115
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:13,010
Fine,

116
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:14,330
go in and watch me pee!

117
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:26,570
Let's go.

118
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:28,090
Let go of me!

119
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:29,850
Let go!

120
00:06:29,900 --> 00:06:30,620
Shen Dongyang.

121
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:31,410
Let go of me.

122
00:06:31,420 --> 00:06:32,610
You abandoned my sister.

123
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:34,130
I won't let you get away with this!

124
00:06:58,660 --> 00:06:59,450
Take him away!

125
00:07:19,140 --> 00:07:20,890
Who are you here to guard, exactly?

126
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:23,090
I didn't see you protecting me just now!

127
00:07:23,620 --> 00:07:24,210
Miss Xu,

128
00:07:25,780 --> 00:07:26,330
let's head back.

129
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:28,130
Let go of me!

130
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:33,090
Isn't that

131
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:36,050
Xu Yawei, the second daughter of Gangcheng's Xu family?

132
00:07:36,420 --> 00:07:37,770
I almost didn't recognize her.

133
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:39,490
Who's the other guy?

134
00:07:39,780 --> 00:07:41,490
I think he's her new bodyguard.

135
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:43,970
A bodyguard?

136
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:45,340
Doesn't seem like it.

137
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:48,010
A bodyguard looks like that?

138
00:07:48,620 --> 00:07:49,730
I heard he's an ex-military man

139
00:07:49,820 --> 00:07:50,730
from the north.

140
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:52,890
Someone tempted Xu Yawei

141
00:07:52,900 --> 00:07:53,850
into using opium.

142
00:07:54,300 --> 00:07:55,570
After Xu Zhenghai found out,

143
00:07:55,980 --> 00:07:57,450
he hired an ex-soldier as a bodyguard

144
00:07:57,460 --> 00:07:58,370
to keep an eye on her.

145
00:07:58,580 --> 00:08:00,250
Like her, Yingxian is also

146
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:03,330
a rich young lady,

147
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:05,370
but she never goes astray.

148
00:08:12,940 --> 00:08:13,650
What do you think

149
00:08:14,380 --> 00:08:15,570
people like us should do

150
00:08:16,060 --> 00:08:17,250
if something we're interested in

151
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:18,610
just so happens to belong

152
00:08:19,180 --> 00:08:19,850
to someone else?

153
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:21,810
So what if it belongs to someone else?

154
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:23,450
Just buy it.

155
00:08:24,020 --> 00:08:26,140
Even if the owner refuses to sell,

156
00:08:27,060 --> 00:08:29,250
it's not impossible to take it by force.

157
00:08:30,740 --> 00:08:31,530
You're right.

158
00:08:31,940 --> 00:08:34,090
It's not impossible to take it by force.

159
00:08:37,580 --> 00:08:38,220
Tell me.

160
00:08:38,940 --> 00:08:40,170
What's caught your eye this time?

161
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:41,770
I'll help you get it.

162
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:43,890
For something like this,

163
00:08:44,220 --> 00:08:45,490
it's better to handle it myself.

164
00:08:46,820 --> 00:08:48,100
Thanks to Miss Xu,

165
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:49,690
this year's banquet

166
00:08:49,820 --> 00:08:51,370
is more interesting than usual.

167
00:08:51,820 --> 00:08:53,610
You're just a bodyguard my father hired,

168
00:08:53,860 --> 00:08:55,140
a lackey.

169
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:56,570
What are you doing?

170
00:08:56,820 --> 00:08:57,770
I just want to have some fun.

171
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:01,370
What are you doing?

172
00:09:01,780 --> 00:09:02,570
Miss Xu,

173
00:09:02,740 --> 00:09:03,770
don't have fun

174
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:05,090
by touching things you shouldn't.

175
00:09:26,260 --> 00:09:26,850
Miss,

176
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:28,850
you've stepped on the lighter.

177
00:09:29,860 --> 00:09:30,490
Have I?

178
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:33,810
Well, after you pick it up,

179
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:35,490
could you light my cigar for me?

180
00:10:05,420 --> 00:10:05,970
What,

181
00:10:07,020 --> 00:10:07,970
is it your first time lighting a cigar?

182
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:12,370
It's my first time seeing a woman smoke a cigar.

183
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:08,170
Has anyone ever told you

184
00:11:08,780 --> 00:11:10,570
that your back is like a ruler?

185
00:11:11,580 --> 00:11:13,330
It even stays perfectly straight when you bend down.

186
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,250
No.

187
00:11:16,740 --> 00:11:17,970
Thank you for protecting me earlier.

188
00:11:19,740 --> 00:11:21,010
Little does Fu Cheng know

189
00:11:21,740 --> 00:11:24,210
that the next time he sees this cigar-smoking woman,

190
00:11:24,700 --> 00:11:27,410
it will be in an even more awkward situation.

191
00:11:38,700 --> 00:11:40,450
Boss, your brother's in trouble!

192
00:11:43,180 --> 00:11:43,850
Where is he now?

193
00:11:44,020 --> 00:11:44,850
[Haicheng Hotel]
In your hotel room.

194
00:11:51,260 --> 00:11:52,170
Yingxian.

195
00:11:52,900 --> 00:11:54,090
[Jiang Yingqi, youngest son of Gangcheng's Jiang family]
Help me, please.

196
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:55,610
If Dad finds out, I'm finished.

197
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:57,450
Get up.

198
00:11:58,260 --> 00:11:59,050
What happened?

199
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:01,570
It's all because of Lu Xuan.

200
00:12:01,820 --> 00:12:05,490
[Lu Xuan, illegitimate son of Lu Ying, Deputy Commander of Nanli]
Jiang Yingqi, you've got a nice new car.

201
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:07,330
If you like it, Mr. Lu,

202
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:09,050
you can have it.

203
00:12:09,220 --> 00:12:10,650
Jiang Yingqi, have you lost your mind?

204
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:13,050
Why would you try to please the illegitimate son of a mere deputy commander?

205
00:12:13,290 --> 00:12:14,930
Lu Xuan got into a car accident.

206
00:12:15,460 --> 00:12:16,290
The car

207
00:12:16,740 --> 00:12:17,930
was yours.

208
00:12:20,420 --> 00:12:21,930
If it were that simple,

209
00:12:22,180 --> 00:12:23,250
you wouldn't be this scared.

210
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:24,810
What really happened?

211
00:12:27,940 --> 00:12:30,170
That night, Lu Xuan left a private party

212
00:12:30,180 --> 00:12:31,330
with a girl.

213
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:33,690
They were both drunk,

214
00:12:34,140 --> 00:12:35,410
and they got into an argument.

215
00:12:37,100 --> 00:12:37,850
Then...

216
00:12:57,540 --> 00:12:57,930
Yingxian...

217
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,450
- Yingxian, I'm so sorry! - And a journalist took pictures too?

218
00:13:01,580 --> 00:13:02,730
If we weren't family,

219
00:13:03,540 --> 00:13:05,090
I'd really shoot you right now, you idiot!

220
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:10,210
Ke Rui, call the Shen family.

221
00:13:10,300 --> 00:13:10,780
Got it.

222
00:13:18,900 --> 00:13:20,170
[Haicheng Hospital]
How's the girl now?

223
00:13:21,780 --> 00:13:23,610
She's severely injured and still in surgery.

224
00:13:24,180 --> 00:13:26,010
Boss, to be honest,

225
00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:27,810
any other Jiang family member

226
00:13:27,980 --> 00:13:29,250
wouldn't bother saving her.

227
00:13:29,780 --> 00:13:30,850
Once she wakes up,

228
00:13:31,220 --> 00:13:32,450
there will be a lot of trouble.

229
00:13:32,860 --> 00:13:33,650
She's been to one

230
00:13:33,660 --> 00:13:35,090
of Lu Xuan's private gatherings.

231
00:13:36,060 --> 00:13:36,610
So,

232
00:13:37,340 --> 00:13:38,290
even you've been infected

233
00:13:38,340 --> 00:13:40,370
with my family's cold-heartedness, huh?

234
00:13:43,580 --> 00:13:44,570
How is Lu Xuan now?

235
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:45,850
He broke a rib

236
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:47,090
and had surgery last night.

237
00:13:47,860 --> 00:13:49,730
With another two weeks of rest, he'll be discharged.

238
00:13:50,620 --> 00:13:51,530
How's the Lu family reacting?

239
00:13:51,980 --> 00:13:53,210
They know they're in the wrong.

240
00:13:53,540 --> 00:13:55,290
Mr. Shen helped suppress the news

241
00:13:55,420 --> 00:13:56,450
and kept it from going public.

242
00:13:56,860 --> 00:13:58,610
Our only worry now is the girl and her family.

243
00:13:59,140 --> 00:14:00,450
As long as they stay quiet...

244
00:14:00,900 --> 00:14:02,210
Have you found her details?

245
00:14:02,860 --> 00:14:03,770
It took some effort,

246
00:14:03,900 --> 00:14:04,810
but I got them.

247
00:14:05,700 --> 00:14:06,530
Her name is Fu Zhi.

248
00:14:07,060 --> 00:14:07,930
Her mother passed away young,

249
00:14:07,980 --> 00:14:09,370
and her father's been missing for years.

250
00:14:09,860 --> 00:14:10,970
She has an older brother named Fu Cheng.

251
00:14:11,060 --> 00:14:11,930
He enlisted at 18

252
00:14:12,100 --> 00:14:14,010
and made it to the top class in just one year.

253
00:14:14,460 --> 00:14:15,930
He's participated in many special operations.

254
00:14:50,540 --> 00:14:51,530
It's him.

255
00:15:05,020 --> 00:15:05,900
Why didn't he

256
00:15:06,660 --> 00:15:08,140
choose to stay in the military

257
00:15:08,220 --> 00:15:09,180
and climb the ranks?

258
00:15:09,380 --> 00:15:10,420
Why leave the army

259
00:15:10,660 --> 00:15:12,380
to become a bodyguard?

260
00:15:38,740 --> 00:15:39,860
♪You've set off♪

261
00:15:39,980 --> 00:15:42,860
♪To warm another world♪

262
00:15:43,260 --> 00:15:44,260
♪I've stopped♪

263
00:15:44,380 --> 00:15:47,980
♪But never said goodbye to the past♪

264
00:15:48,260 --> 00:15:50,620
♪Watching you leave, I mourn, and sorrow lingers♪

265
00:15:50,820 --> 00:15:53,180
♪Tears of regret, pain running deep♪

266
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:57,100
♪You've gone to a world that isn't yours♪

267
00:15:57,290 --> 00:16:02,180
♪Here's a song for the passersby of life♪

268
00:16:02,420 --> 00:16:07,300
♪When you listen, will you tear up?♪

269
00:16:07,540 --> 00:16:10,620
♪The past has been cremated♪

270
00:16:10,650 --> 00:16:15,740
♪Placed in the urn of my heart♪

271
00:16:17,580 --> 00:16:19,340
♪Crying, I say♪

272
00:16:19,540 --> 00:16:23,100
♪I'm not afraid anymore. I've forgotten the hurt♪

273
00:16:23,260 --> 00:16:25,580
♪You, singing a song♪

274
00:16:25,780 --> 00:16:28,180
♪Stand barefoot in the river of my life♪

275
00:16:28,300 --> 00:16:30,700
♪The past has been cremated♪

276
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:35,820
♪No longer relying on anyone to live♪

277
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:01,020
♪You understand now, right?♪

278
00:17:01,180 --> 00:17:03,700
♪I think you do♪

279
00:17:03,900 --> 00:17:05,180
♪The novelty of it all♪

280
00:17:05,340 --> 00:17:08,660
♪Only becomes scary once it fades♪

281
00:17:09,100 --> 00:17:11,460
♪Turns out, even deities have cried♪

282
00:17:11,620 --> 00:17:13,980
♪Pitying us and our foolish lives♪

283
00:17:14,180 --> 00:17:18,020
♪I respect the final choice you made♪

284
00:17:18,180 --> 00:17:22,900
♪Here's a song for the passersby of life♪

285
00:17:23,220 --> 00:17:28,180
♪When you listen, will you tear up?♪

286
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:31,380
♪The past has been cremated♪

287
00:17:31,470 --> 00:17:36,660
♪Placed in the urn of my heart♪

288
00:17:38,540 --> 00:17:40,220
♪Crying, I say♪

289
00:17:40,300 --> 00:17:44,060
♪I'm not afraid anymore. I've forgotten the hurt♪

290
00:17:44,140 --> 00:17:46,540
♪You, singing a song♪

291
00:17:46,660 --> 00:17:48,100
♪Stand barefoot in the river of my life♪
